title: AskyBlock插件问题
author: 是橘不是兔
txt_content:
玩家输入创建岛屿 然后岛屿重叠为其他玩家 这个应该怎么改YY_QX issued server command: /is[18:52:20 INFO]: [ASkyBlock] Found solid block at island height - adding to islands.yml 0,-400
[18:52:20 WARN]: [ASkyBlock] *** Duplicate or overlapping islands! ***

replies.author: wjwrh
replies.txt_content:
把你askyblock的config.yml前两个配置发上来看看
就是那个岛屿保护范围和岛屿距离那个
你把askyblock的玩家数据删掉，空岛世界删掉，然后开服后应该就能解决了

replies.txt_content:
